                            <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> der </del> ʒü Stercʒelbach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l5">der vns <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſprechen</expan> ſulle
                        ſteen <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc . daʒ haben vvir
                        vvol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l6">
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Nu wiſſen vvir nÿemant beÿ vns der <del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_591_line_1592207754623_4213"><expan>Morg<ex>enſtern</ex></expan>
